creator: Beyond Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Beyond is a fast and fun way to chat and meet Tourist and National.

Start your holiday in the right WAY!
Chatting and Meeting national friends in a new way.
No signup required. One click and all ready to chat.


CHAT 💬
• Tap on the type of users you want to chat with. Tourist or National.
• See all available users of the type of users you want to chat with.
• Click on one user and start chatting.

CITY 🗺
• Chat with users in another city.
• Prepare your holiday friends before your Trip.
• Find Tour Guide in your destination holiday before your Trip.

DISCOVER 🔍
• Discover new places to visit in your current city.
• Share new places you discover during your holiday.
• Find popular places for party in your city.

TOUR GUIDE 🗺
• Find a tour guide to show you around during you staying.

FRIENDSHIP 👥
• Automatically save all friends you have made while chatting.
• Make best friend before your trip.

Beyond Simplicity , Enjoy New Cities!
descriptionShort: Chat with TOURIST in your city, no signup required.

title: Beyond - Chat With Tourist, Book Tours.

creator: Beyond Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Beyond is the most reliable way to connect to your local guide and vice versa.

- INTRODUCTION -

Welcome on board. This Platform aiming Tourists willing to find a new mate to hangout with while on vacation on a foreign land. That new mate could be a tour guide or any local.

- POLING -

To be visible on the map, you will need to create a pole. A Pole on Beyond is a point on the map which indicate the type of connections the creator is aiming for.

- BOOKINGS -

Book Tour from a certified Local Guide. Beyond App verified and certified Local Guide based on several factors. You can Trust verified Local Guide on Beyond App.

- COMMUNICATION -

Request, Connect and chat with anyone you want to pole with. Chat and notification channel will ease your communication flow. Beyond App also has an auto group creation which is set by your pole type if you wish to have a group instead.

DISCOVER 🔍
• Discover new places to visit in your current city.
• Share new places you discover during your holiday.
• Find popular places for party in your city.

TOUR GUIDE 🗺
• Find a Tours Guide to show you around during you staying.

FRIENDSHIP 👥
• Automatically save all friends you have made while chatting.
• Make your personal Tour Guide before your trip.

Beyond a city , there is a Tourist!
descriptionShort: Meet your local guide or MAKE ONE!

Welcome on board. This Platform aiming Tourists willing to find a new mate to hangout with while on vacation on a foreign land. That new mate could be a tour guide or any local.

- POLING -

To be visible on the map, you will need to create a pole. A Pole on Beyond is a point on the map which indicate the type of connections the creator is aiming for.

- BOOKINGS -

Book Tour from a certified Local Guide. Beyond App verified and certified Local Guide based on several factors.

- COMMUNICATION -

Request, Connect and chat with anyone you want to pole with. Chat and notification channel will ease your communication flow.

- MEETUP GROUP -

Turn your poling to a meetup point. Setup the type of polers you want to have in your meet up group.
descriptionShort: Meet your local guide or MAKE ONE!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: All bugs have been exterminated. You may continue poling on your favorite activity.
